{"tid":935454,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"自己折磨自己:(","createTime":"2018-12-10T04:29:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T08:20:16.000Z","uid":225088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e73775a5aac13380b80f0bb1aa69ed0e4096186","tid":935454,"uid":225088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T04:29:46.000Z","msg":"同男朋友分左手之後 我問佢可唔可以一齊返<br />\n點知佢又答可以 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n復合返既第一日就發現佢玩返Skout <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一直都無出聲 扮無野 <br />\n但實際左回佢wtsapp 速度已經慢左同冷淡左<br />\n(平時係佢冷淡我）<br />\n依家佢就一直wtsapp 我 又報返行縱咁 <br />\n<br />\n琴日見完佢，佢黎地鐵站接我<br />\n又好用力咁攬住我，拖實我隻手唔放 <br />\n是但講左句我想要隻比卡超八達通 即刻除左送比我<br />\n臨走前佢仲同我講 愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n一個男人一邊玩Skout 識女女 一邊就對你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心好痛 <br />\n玩死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd36512232408a0d21bc063ccd7cbdd7bb08c90e","tid":935454,"uid":166827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T04:43:32.000Z","msg":"其實識仔"},{"pid":"926a1c9bf273f52791aa31f55c9e6af4c80b3a57","tid":935454,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.msgweb.nl/emoticons/tongue_smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.msgweb.nl%2Femoticons%2Ftongue_smile.gif&h=20237091&s={SIZE}\" />有意外驚喜"},{"pid":"341cc84e93d2070c431c2b6b2e76aa0b2229fa9b","tid":935454,"uid":225088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"926a1c9bf273f52791aa31f55c9e6af4c80b3a57","tid":935454,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.msgweb.nl/emoticons/tongue_smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.msgweb.nl%2Femoticons%2Ftongue_smile.gif